data.description: SO much newness! Move in ready! New hvac, new water heater, newly renovated en-suite bathroom in primary. Welcome to this charming single-level, all brick ranch home in Nashville's vibrant Donelson neighborhood. This 3-bed, 2-bath home opens to dramatic vaulted ceilings in the living room, a cozy wood burning fireplace, and finished hardwood floors and tile in wet areas. The updated kitchen includes white cabinets, white marble countertops, and plenty of natural light through the bay windows off the dining room. The primary bedroom features a renovated en suite bathroom with new floors, vanity, a frameless glass shower door, and bluetooth enabled fan to connect your music. Outside, a spacious 11x20 deck overlooks the fully fenced back yard, perfect for pets and entertaining. Nestled on a peaceful cul-de-sac street, this home offers quick access to the interstate, Percy Priest lake, Stones River Greenway, BNA Airport, and shopping. Refrigerator, washer, and dryer convey.
